org.batfish.symbolic.smt

Class PropertyChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.symbolic.smt.PropertyChecker

  • public class PropertyChecker
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of functions to check if various properties hold in the network. The general idea is to create a new encoder object for the network, instrument additional properties on top of the model, and then assert the negation of the property of interest.
